  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bae\u0bc2\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0bae\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0baa\u0baf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b86\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Public Utilities Commission has released a list of power cuts for the next three days",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission of Sri Lanka has published the list of power outages in the country from tomorrow to 08th.",
        "Sri Lanka Public Utilities Commission Chairman Janaka Ratnayake has said that power cuts will be implemented for 3 hours for the next three days.",
        "Accordingly, for Zones A, B, C, D, E, F, G, H, I, J, K, L, P, Q, R, S, T, U, V, W, 1 hour and 40 minutes in day work, It has been reported that there will be a power cut for 1 hour and 20 minutes during the night.",
        "In addition, power cut will be enforced for 2 hours and 30 minutes from 6 am to 8.30 am in Colombo metropolitan area.",
        "Meanwhile, Janaka Ratnayake has also informed that power cut will be implemented for 3 hours from 5.30 am to 8.30 am in M, N, O, X, Y and Z zones."
      ],
